{"tid":1467923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［大鑊］環球時報記者付國豪送院途中腦出血不治","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:59:23.000Z","uid":14678,"like":6,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea3a952080b5014488bca5112211fb3f9884cb5","tid":1467923,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:43:23.000Z","msg":"首先，對唔住，我係標題黨。（有錯就要真誠道歉）Be Humble<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人諗過如果今晚出咗呢單新聞會點？<br />\n呢場運動即時玩完，係即時！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係呢到又要再提一提大家，天琦講過咩<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好比你嘅仇恨支配咗你嘅理性</strong></span></span><br />\n今晚機場發生過咩事我就唔詳細講啦<br />\n我想問到底點解我地要堵塞機場？今晚係捉鬼大會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. 徹底撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放義士<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家係唔係唔記得咗？唔緊要，唔記得嘅請而家同我背咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係，無錯。我個人認為今晚係輸得好徹底<br />\n原因係：大家只係掛住同記得捉鬼<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，拋諸腦後</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係嘅，而家同大家講你身邊有鬼，係會驚嘅。但如果我同你講，其實啲鬼由6月9號開始就已經係你身邊，咁點解你而家先驚？而家先嚟捉？被人影大頭一直都有，但點解你之前唔會綁起個人？我希望你地每位都問一問自己。點解我地嘅Dress Code係<span style=\"color: navy;\">Block Bloc</span>?<br />\n<br />\n對於前線嘅手足，我無咩要求，我只係希望你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係行動之前，比個腦冷靜下10秒</span></span>，不過救手足就唔好諗啦，救到就救啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n諗一諗你下一步嘅行動值唔值得同埋可能嘅結果就夠了。我明白前線情緒係會高漲會唔穩定，但係你停一停，諗一諗，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">呢個世界唔係人地話咩就係咩，你要有你自己嘅獨立思考同分析！</span></span> 如果你覺得唔對路嘅，即閃又或者請提出你嘅諗法，再同大家傾，以免跟錯人。（所以如果你覺我唔啱就負皮上一頁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n最後都想同前線手足講一句，我地有樣嘢同黑警係無分別架。就係一個累全家<br />\n但係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>We are a team, and the better team. </strong></span></span> <br />\n就算你地前線放核彈炸死哂啲狗，我地都<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>絕不分割</strong></span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">錫春袋另計</span><br />\n<br />\n係機場嘅手足，Be humble, Be Polite. 講多兩句Sorry, 解釋下比遊客聽係唔洗死架<br />\n最後，文宜組，係時候開工收復失地啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c01df91ff255a0c977bbdf9644162f152d67516","tid":1467923,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:45:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2576913a0167de71fd2614c3a1a45ed813b3e602","tid":1467923,"uid":4139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:31.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n唔好意思 忍唔到"},{"pid":"581aab2bca222df6c7134dec4b40175677d9cfa2","tid":1467923,"uid":155374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母標題黨到咁<br />\n完全執鎖</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a9a31b45dc73d97cb92ab250df6b1d25fb6c50b9","tid":1467923,"uid":197010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"前線成日話要和理非 BUY 前線做野<br />\n點解前線永遠都唔 BUY 和理非做既野?"},{"pid":"ae7277c0945dfcae01ffa4dc141cbe7582e53228","tid":1467923,"uid":230861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:39.000Z","msg":"屌咪撚標題黨啦"},{"pid":"4ac7110a2049ed520885db455c72952fe8d5095c","tid":1467923,"uid":155374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母標題黨到咁<br />\n完全封鎖</span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"36b44d26e3e779eca8f9998f0b31ffbc80960c98","tid":1467923,"uid":158889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9a31b45dc73d97cb92ab250df6b1d25fb6c50b9","tid":1467923,"uid":197010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"前線成日話要和理非 BUY 前線做野<br />\n點解前線永遠都唔 BUY 和理非做既野?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"因為無和理非出黎囉 今日d 人呢？"},{"pid":"5c82660e98d6c232b5b5afe0067e70c8cc4a9faa","tid":1467923,"uid":293225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母開心咗兩秒<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母淨係叫人冷靜?<br />\n冷靜嘅就無71攻入立會讀宣言啦."},{"pid":"ceb8c82ea1af56700048106af116e961b370cc23","tid":1467923,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"無論和理非定勇武 必須遵守<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 不打記者 <br />\n2. 不打救護<br />\n3. 不濫用酷刑 <br />\n4. 不攻擊平民</span></span>"},{"pid":"e6561c6d6eb909141e5d6e7ada705b7c3807133d","tid":1467923,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:50:53.000Z","msg":"你老母就真係傷重不治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeb37222ec936e06bf2a9a2ba9540967b4cfd86","tid":1467923,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請善用不推文回覆功能屌樓主</span></span>"},{"pid":"c9d55fd6e9d07210512ac70a2418af8354d32ccf","tid":1467923,"uid":19728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:51:38.000Z","msg":"憑你係標題黨就可以完全封鎖"},{"pid":"aa4d99558b3409962e59c0ba406cc9f5149d8671","tid":1467923,"uid":169198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:53:46.000Z","msg":"屌你啦 最撚憎標題黨<br />\n見到第一句已經唔撚想睇"},{"pid":"a794576e16a68dd388631deb571d6704b33010e4","tid":1467923,"uid":77137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"sor你老母咩<br />\n一定要咁樣搶focus呃人聽你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d3965eb7a5aa7cd9ccb2cc1cc4581786540d63","tid":1467923,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:19.000Z","msg":"條友28歲, 搵鬼信呀"},{"pid":"4ea5544cad64a664a3ef9454c8b627f1dc4f8acf","ti